1
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:23,800
The kid's grown up now.

2
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:26,920
He deserves an explanation.

3
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:34,520
Little brother.

4
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:37,080
What's wrong?

5
00:01:38,960 --> 00:01:40,920
Tell me what's bothering you.

6
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:44,280
What happened?

7
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:49,560
Lin You.

8
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:51,240
Are you okay?

9
00:01:53,880 --> 00:01:55,200
Did you two have a fight?

10
00:02:00,080 --> 00:02:01,160
That's so weird.

11
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,480
How much did they offer you?

12
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:15,160
Are you that desperate for money?

13
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:17,760
What's the real reason?

14
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:18,600
Enough.

15
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,120
Stop talking.

16
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,080
This is my own shop.

17
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:25,200
Selling it is none of your business.

18
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:26,560
Little girl.

19
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:28,120
Do you even know who I am?

20
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,440
Listen here, old man.

21
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:31,360
Don't think your dirty secrets are safe.

22
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:33,600
Today, I'm going in to see for myself.

23
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,280
I'll let the whole village know.

24
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:36,880
Liu Guilan lives right here.

25
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,920
Her husband's name is Zhou Dahai.

26
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,280
And she has a child too.

27
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,000
Shut up!

28
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:47,080
Why do you even care?

29
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:48,240
We're already here.

30
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:52,680
Master sold off Daji.

31
00:02:54,600 --> 00:02:55,400
What?

32
00:03:51,040 --> 00:03:51,880
Miss Liu Liu.

33
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:56,120
What?

34
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:57,640
You don't recognize me?

35
00:03:58,160 --> 00:03:58,880
No, I don't.

36
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,960
Didn't we just meet?

37
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:01,920
In Jixiang Village.

38
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,680
I'll get straight to the point.

39
00:04:08,480 --> 00:04:10,760
I know there's something you must do.

40
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:14,000
I can help you.

41
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:16,399
In whatever way you want.

42
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,320
Hey, Liu Liu.

43
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:53,960
When?

44
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:57,880
Okay.

45
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:11,360
From now on, whatever you do at Daji,

46
00:05:12,280 --> 00:05:13,200
I won't interfere.

47
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,120
You'll see for yourself

48
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:23,680
what kind of people they really are.

49
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:32,920
Why'd you suddenly ask me here?

50
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:38,800
Didn't you

51
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:41,640
let Yaoyao visit your secret base before?

52
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:50,960
This is...

53
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:59,160
When Yaoyao had her accident,

54
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,520
I knew she hadn't left.

55
00:06:04,080 --> 00:06:05,320
No one believed me,

56
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:07,880
including my own parents.

57
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:10,480
Although

58
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:12,880
they never cared about me anyway.

59
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,520
During that time,

60
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:20,200
I felt really awful.

61
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:22,480
My emotions were all over the place.

62
00:06:29,400 --> 00:06:30,520
Luckily, later on,

63
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,280
I met Master.

64
00:06:33,840 --> 00:06:35,040
He was the only one who believed me.

65
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:38,800
He even performed a ritual for me

66
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:40,760
to help calm me down.

67
00:06:41,520 --> 00:06:43,080
And I gradually got better.

68
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:46,600
Then I stayed at Daji,

69
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:49,080
got to know Zhou Yi,

70
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:52,200
and met you too.

71
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:04,240
My time at Daji

72
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:07,280
has been the happiest, other than

73
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,280
the days I spent with Yaoyao.

74
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:15,480
Why bring all this up suddenly?

75
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:21,880
Weren't you the one who said it?

76
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:25,480
Letting the people who care about you

77
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:26,840
know your past

78
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:29,880
helps them get closer to you.

79
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:38,520
Yaoyao told you that?

80
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,160
I was just thinking,

81
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:47,800
if I hadn't

82
00:07:48,520 --> 00:07:49,760
gone behind Master's back

83
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:52,280
to meddle in Jixiang Village's affairs,

84
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:54,080
maybe

85
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,200
we'd have figured out

86
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:58,400
why Master wanted to sell Daji.

87
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,560
Maybe we could've stopped him.

88
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,360
Don't say that.

89
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:06,000
We decided it together.

90
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:07,160
Besides,

91
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:09,880
you just wanted Uncle Wang to make more.

92
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:11,560
What's more,

93
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:14,120
Uncle Wang has his own unspoken reasons.

94
00:08:20,520 --> 00:08:22,080
Anyway, Daji's been sold,

95
00:08:22,640 --> 00:08:23,960
and I have to go back too.

96
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:27,720
Putting everything else aside,

97
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:31,160
Zhou Yi has Master,

98
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:32,200
and Sister Bai too.

99
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:35,280
But us,

100
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,640
we have nothing.

101
00:08:53,880 --> 00:08:55,400
But it's okay, Lin You.

102
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,640
From now on, when you do things,

103
00:09:01,280 --> 00:09:02,680
don't be so impulsive.

104
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:06,520
And don't worry about how others see you

105
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:07,520
or what they think.

106
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:12,040
Because the way you are right now

107
00:09:12,400 --> 00:09:13,960
is the best version of you.

108
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:22,200
I...

109
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:25,280
The reason I asked you here today

110
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,960
and told you so much about my past

111
00:09:31,560 --> 00:09:34,120
is so you can truly get to know me again.

112
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:35,160
At least,

113
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:37,880
at least when you think of me later,

114
00:09:39,040 --> 00:09:40,360
you won't just remember me as

115
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:42,200
that crazy Xu Liu Liu.

116
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:54,800
Lin You,

117
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,280
getting to know you

118
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:02,440
has truly made me happy.

119
00:10:04,640 --> 00:10:06,280
What you said to Yaoyao,

120
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,640
I heard all of it.

121
00:10:21,560 --> 00:10:22,280
Thank you.

122
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:27,560
Truly, thank you.

123
00:10:32,520 --> 00:10:34,720
Yaoyao would definitely be happy too.

124
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:10,640
This music box,

125
00:11:11,280 --> 00:11:11,960
it's for you.

126
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:15,760
Yaoyao asked me to give it to you.

127
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:19,320
Consider it her way of accepting you.

128
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:38,960
Lin You.

129
00:11:40,400 --> 00:11:41,840
Take a picture of me here, will you?

130
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:44,320
Right here.

131
00:12:07,160 --> 00:12:09,000
Then draw me into your comics again,

132
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:12,640
because your comics

133
00:12:13,800 --> 00:12:15,240
always have happy endings.

134
00:12:17,520 --> 00:12:19,120
I hope when I'm old

135
00:12:19,280 --> 00:12:20,720
I can look at your comics

136
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:23,520
and just like Master,

137
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:25,400
say with confidence,

138
00:12:26,560 --> 00:12:28,960
"I was beautiful when I was young too!"

139
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:38,400
Don't worry.

140
00:12:40,640 --> 00:12:42,320
Heaven wouldn't be so cruel

141
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:43,840
as to hurt

142
00:12:44,040 --> 00:12:45,680
a gentle, beautiful girl like you.

143
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,000
Here's the photo.

144
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:11,040
Liu Liu.

145
00:13:11,040 --> 00:13:12,280
I think I know why Old Wang

146
00:13:12,280 --> 00:13:13,560
wanted to sell Daji.

147
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:15,680
I have to head back to Daji now

148
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:16,920
to confirm a few things.

149
00:13:17,280 --> 00:13:18,400
You should head home early.

150
00:13:18,520 --> 00:13:20,400
Visit Zhou Yi at Sister Bai's tomorrow.

151
00:13:21,640 --> 00:13:22,440
Okay.

152
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,480
Well, you'd better get going then.

153
00:13:24,640 --> 00:13:25,120
Okay.

154
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:59,640
I actually asked Old Wang before

155
00:13:59,880 --> 00:14:00,880
about my parents.

156
00:14:01,520 --> 00:14:02,800
But every time, he'd say

157
00:14:03,160 --> 00:14:04,840
that I was either struck by lightning,

158
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:07,080
or picked out of a trash can.

159
00:14:08,880 --> 00:14:10,280
But come to think of it,

160
00:14:10,680 --> 00:14:11,640
no matter who they were,

161
00:14:12,400 --> 00:14:13,440
having a kid like me,

162
00:14:13,640 --> 00:14:15,760
born with a heart condition,

163
00:14:17,080 --> 00:14:18,440
anyone would've walked away.

164
00:15:23,640 --> 00:15:24,360
Dad.

165
00:15:25,960 --> 00:15:26,680
Mom.

166
00:15:36,280 --> 00:15:37,000
So it turns out

167
00:15:37,800 --> 00:15:40,440
I wasn't an unwanted child after all.

168
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:16,160
Lin You.

169
00:16:18,280 --> 00:16:19,320
Something happened to Zhou Yi.

170
00:16:19,680 --> 00:16:20,600
He's at the hospital.
